videos.description: UConn's Megan Walker heats up from the outside, knocking down 3-pointers from the same corner on back-to-back possessions.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One_Play (Walker sinks 3s from same spot on consecutive possessions) 2020/02/22

videos.headline: Walker sinks 3s from same spot on consecutive possessions

videos.description: UConn forces a turnover with a double team on defense, and Megan Walker passes ahead to Crystal Dangerfield for the easy transition layup.
videos.headline: UConn turns defense into offense

videos.description: Megan Walker dishes a cross-court pass to Anna Makurat, who drains the 3-pointer from the corner despite a defender in her face.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Makurat buries contested triple for UConn) 2020/02/22

videos.headline: Makurat buries contested triple for UConn

videos.description: Anna Makurat pulls up from several feet behind the 3-point line and sinks the shot to increase UConn's lead.
videos.headline: Makurat connects from way downtown

videos.description: UCF's Masseny Kaba accidentally elbows Olivia Nelson-Ododa in the face, forcing the UConn forward to leave the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn's Nelson-Ododa exits after taking elbow to face) 2020/02/22

videos.headline: UConn's Nelson-Ododa exits after taking elbow to face

videos.description: Anna Makurat banks home an and-1 bucket to stop an 8-0 UCF run and give UConn a 13-point lead late.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Makurat's and-1 basket ices game for Huskies) 2020/02/22
